response><xhtml><p><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><LI><FONT FACE="Arial Unicode MS,Arial,Helvetica" SIZE="12" COLOR="#0B333C" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Tell the family that since Mr. Marlboro had not indicated to you that he wanted a do-not-resuscitate order should he become incapable of making that decision himself, the CCU staff initiated a full resuscitation effort  and followed established protocols. Everything was done to resuscitate Mr. Marlboro, but he was unresponsive to those efforts. The resuscitation effort was stopped when it was clear that further efforts would be futile.</FONT></LI></TEXTFORMAT>]]></p></xhtml></response></openquestion></event></studyguide>